body_html:
uninstalling Protobuf 3.6 and pip installing Protobuf 3.4.0 as per the above instructions but importing tensorflow still yields same error message about TypeError: init() got an unexpected keyword argument 'serialized_option

Instailling Protobuf==3.4 gives this error:

tensorflow 1.11.0 has requirement protobuf>=3.6.0, but you'll have protobuf 3.4.0 which is incompatible.

So using the most up-to-date version of Tensorflow requires protobuf>-3.6.0 but using that version yields a serialized_option error. What to do?
